    public class DummiesExecutor

      • executeDummy

        public void executeDummy(DummyThread dummy)
        This method submits a DummyThread object into the pool executor and increases in one the size of the core pool.
        Parameters:
        dummy - the DummyThread object. The method DummyThread.call() is called by this ThreadPoolExecutor.
        See Also:
        AbstractExecutorService.submit(java.util.concurrent.Callable), ThreadPoolExecutor.setCorePoolSize(int)
